high_descs: Face right and go to the cabinet on the left against the wall.
Pick up the empty toilet paper tube from the top of the cabinet.
Turn right and carry the empty tube to the toilet.
Stand the tube on the back of the toilet.
Go to the left side of the toilet and face the wall.
Pick up the empty toilet paper tube from the floor to the left of the toilet.
Carry the tube around to the right side of the toilet.
Stand the tube on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Move two empty toilet paper tubes to the back of a toilet.

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the white shelf.
Pick up the empty toilet paper roll from the white shelf.
Turn around completely and go forward then left then turn right again to face the toilet. .
Set the toilet paper roll on the back end of the toilet.
Turn to the left and go around to the other side of the toilet.
Pick up the empty toilet paper roll from the floor.
Go around to the other side of the toilet
Set the toilet paper roll on the back end of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Move two empty toilet paper roll to the back end of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the white cabinet on the left.
Pick the empty toilet roll up from the cabinet.
Turn around and cross the room to stand on the right side of the toilet.
Put the empty toilet roll on the back of the toilet.
Move to the other side of the toilet and face the floor.
Pick the empty toilet paper roll up from the floor.
Move to the right side of the toilet.
Put the toilet paper roll on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put two toilet paper rolls on the back of a toilet.
